Summary.valueString: The document provides an overview of medical benefits offered by Waterfield Tech, detailing plan choices, costs, and coverage specifics for different health plans including PPO and HDHP options. It outlines deductibles, coinsurance, out-of-pocket maximums, and costs for various services such as physician visits, hospital services, and prescription drugs. Additionally, it includes the monthly cost for different coverage levels effective January 1, 2025.
